channel.title: Starting off
channel.description: Ok my server is good so far but i have 1 problem, I know how to like change your characters starting weapons but everytime i do thats my character goes invisiblw and i dont know how to edit so they can have 100k starting. Could someone please put a code in for like full bronze or just tell me the codes for it and how to put in 100k in inventory?
